 on Amonas, who tried to appease his fears:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

It's sweet and refreshing.
 Almost better than water.
 Drink up, you'll like it.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Amonas was motioning with his head for Hilderich to drink, urging him to
