\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Opportunities may arise once more, don't make me want to take advantage
 of them.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Hilderich opened his mouth wide in what seemed a mock expression of shock
