 woke up feeling refreshed.
 He sat up and flexed his arms and legs, all the time his gaze towards the
 direction of the bullhorns.
 It had been a more than pleasant change to find themselves under the shadow
 of the immense structure that seemed to blot out the suns quite effectively,
 making the whole area have a different feeling all together.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
The one thing they noticed almost immediately was the different climate.
