 happened to him and he would be unable to be there for her.
 More so, especially if something happened to him.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
As luck had brought things about he was far away and out of reach, with
 no means to communicate that he still drew breath.
 His people would probably think him dead, or at the very least running
 for his life, fearful of getting caught.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
