 without some kind of proof, they would eventually silently accept the fact
 that he might not have escaped the clutches of the tyrants.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
If he was being kept alive, reason would dictate that they'd somehow manage
 to know as they usually did and perhaps hope he would still be alive when
 the uprising began in earnest; which if all had been carefully arranged,
 was a matter of days.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
